      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZING MATILDA (2) could not have been more impressive a few runs back in her solid 19.61 win at this track over 342m then has finished in the placings in both runs since. Looks the one to beat on best figures. BINNAWAY WIZARD (5) was strongly fancied last time on the back of a win two back but could only manage fourth (19.99) at this track. Has good box speed and can overcome the tricky draw. Should be about the mark. GOLDEN ZEAL (8) was quickly into stride and found the front last start to record an all-the-way win (19.70) at this track in a Other over 342m. Has good speed and can quickly clear the pack out wide. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. URANA JAM DONUT (7) warrants respect following a recent placing over this course and distance.",
